 - test.sh: halt if ash, cdrecord, mkisofs is not found (gdha, 03/05/2004)
 - cutstream/Makefile: large file system support - fix by Mubashir Cheema
 - rd-base.sh: do a sort -u on md/df.hostname to filter multiple swap entries (gdha, 02/05/2004)
