   and add those lines to md/df.$HOSTNAME - needed for cloning (gdha, 24/04/2004)
 - Config.sh: add BusLogic and pcnet32 to modules list (handy to have standard
   on CD for restore test within VMware) (gdha, 24/04/2004)
 - test.sh: add rsync to the check_exe list for /dev copy to ram disk (gdha, 24/04/2004)
 - clone-dsk.sh: add plenty of code to clone a Software RAID meta-device to a single
   IDE/SCSI device (10-24/04/2004)
