   start with mkCDrec without checking their system and by doing this
   avoiding crying-for-help calls (gdha, 06/06/2002)
 - replaced syslinux-1.63 with v2.00 (gdha, 05/06/2002)
 - rd-base.sh: improve exclude mount-points routines (gdha, 03/12/2002)
 - test.sh: test 2: found part - subver. check for tar/nasm (gdha, 02/12/2002)
 - test.sh: test 2: mkisofs changed into ${MKISOFS} (gdha, 27/11/2002)
 - restore-fs.sh: sometimes error with calculating partition_size when it
   ended with - or +. The - or + is stripped (gdha, 26/11/2002)
 - rd-base.sh/restore_common.sh/restore-fs.sh/tar-it.sh: added support
   for the 'auto' fs-type (SF #640777, gdha, 25/11/2002)
 - initrd.sh: added [ test echo pwd to the binaries list (flyn/gdha)
