   arrays support with cloning (reported by F. Liedekerke, 05/11/2001)
 - restore_common.sh: fix for bugreport #477514 by Ron Yorston (rmyorston)
 - rd-base.sh: improved inits scripting (gdha, 29/10/2001)
 - alt-ctrl-del/ctrl-alt-del: mini-script to reboot system in case busybox
   reboot/halt/shutdown refuses to be usefull (gdha, 28/10/2001)
 - makeISO9660.in: added code mkisofs with isolinux (gdha, 27/10/2001)
 - bootflop.sh: added isolinux steps for memtest86 utility if present,
   code adapt necessary for mkcdrec_utils (next release) gdha 27/10/2001
 - syslinux-1.63: needs isolinux capabilities for memtest86
