 - rd-base.sh line 644: added 'then' (broke the make process!) (02/01/2001)
 - start-restore.sh: removed a ' in the welcome line of mkcdrec
 - rd-base.sh: added cp -R utilities to isofs (29/12/2000)
 - clone-dsk.sh: added code to change /etc/fstab according source/dest. dev
